Insurance Lightning Web Component UI Reference

Insurance Lightning web components provide a layered framework that displays, processes, passes, retrieves, and re-displays information.

The following are top-level Insurance Lightning web components:

* insOsMultiInstance
* insOsProductSelection
* insOsSingleInstance

Other Insurance Lightning web components include:

* insOsConfirmation
* insOsCoverage
* insOsCoverageList
* insOsGrandchildrenProduct
* insOsMultiInstanceChildProducts
* insOsMultiInstanceGrandchildren
* insOsMultiInstanceMatrix
* insOsMultiInstanceMatrixCell
* insOsMultiInstanceModal
* insOsMultiItem
* insOsProductRulesReview
* insOsProductSelection
* insOsSingleInstance
* insProductMatrix
* insProductSummary
* insRecordEditor
* insQuote
* insUtility
